As an artist 👩🏽‍🎨 I control the narrative on modern day art. If you notice 2 things. 1. I usually only paint women. Why? Women are the most beautiful creatures on earth & our beauty should always be celebrated. 2. I only paint women of color unless I am commissioned to paint a Caucasian woman or man. 
Why do I do this? As someone show has studied art , history & media. White skin, due to colonialism & colonialism has always been viewed as the prettier skin tone. The standard of beauty.
